<div class="axil-privacy-area axil-section-gap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-10">
        <div class="axil-privacy-policy">
          <h4 class="title mb-4">Refund & Return Policy</h4>
          <p class="mb-4">
           <strong></strong> We believe in <strong>100% customer satisfaction</strong>. Operated by Harisree Handlooms, our team of dedicated professionals works daily to make your experience special. We understand that finding the right product can take time — and that's why we offer returns and exchanges under certain conditions.
          </p>

          <h5 class="mb-3">General Return & Exchange Conditions</h5>
          <ul class="mb-4">
            <li>Requests must be made <strong>within 7 days</strong> of receiving the parcel.</li>
            <li>A <strong>360-degree opening video</strong> of the package is required when raising a return or exchange request.</li>
            <li><strong>No exchange or return</strong> will be accepted without this video.</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="mb-3">Eligible Cases for Return or Exchange</h5>
          <ul class="mb-4">
            <li>Product defects or damages</li>
            <li>Incorrect product received</li>
            <li>Sizing concerns (if applicable)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4"><strong>Note:</strong> No returns or exchanges will be accepted for any other reasons not mentioned above.</p>

          <h5 class="mb-3">Return & Pickup Process</h5>
          <ul class="mb-4">
            <li>Customers must arrange courier/reverse pickup for the return of the defective or incorrect product.</li>
            <li><strong>Free pickups are not guaranteed</strong>; they are based on mutual agreement.</li>
            <li>If agreed, pickup will be arranged within <strong>7 working days</strong>.</li>
            <li>The exchange process begins once the product is received at our warehouse.</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="mb-3">Product-Specific Policies</h5>
          <ul class="mb-4">
            <li><strong>7 Days Replacement & Exchange Policy</strong></li>
            <li><strong>7 Days Return Policy</strong></li>
            <li>Replacements or exchange products will be delivered within <strong>7 days</strong> of receiving the returned item.</li>
            <li>Approved refunds will be credited to the customer's bank account within <strong>5–7 working days</strong>.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="text-muted">We value your trust in HariSree Handlooms and are always here to help make your shopping experience smooth and satisfying.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

